        <div id="population-results" style="margin-top: 10px;"><div style="padding: 8px; background: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c2c7; border-radius: 3px; color: #842029;">âŒ Found 0 questions in selected categories (out of 1619 total questions). Using taxonomy: ld_quiz_category. Categories: 166</div></div>
